description.S: The Samsung Galaxy S21 FE 128GB Gray 5G combines the best of its predecessor, the Samsung S21 series, with a good price.
The Apple iPhone 14 Pro 128GB Space Black doesn't have a notch anymore.
The OnePlus Nord 2T 256GB Gray 5G is a powerful mid-range smartphone that's very fast with average use.
The Sony Xperia 10 IV 128GB Black 5G is a mid-range smartphone for average use.
Thanks to the large 5050mAh battery, you can use the Nokia G21 128GB Blue the entire day without having to charge in between.
